---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts'
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
    <main>
      <h1>🤡 Hello, It's me!</h1>
      <p>中文：</p>
      <p>
        大家好，我是
        zouhangwithsweet，一个来自中国的软件工程师，目前居住在美国旧金山湾区。我的主要工作是开发和维护大型的云端应用系统。我在软件开发方面拥有多年的经验，掌握了多种编程语言，例如
        Python、JavaScript、TypeScript 等。 除了我的职业生涯，我对人工智能也很感兴趣。我正在学习机器学习和深度学习，并在我的
        GitHub 上分享我的学习笔记和项目，包括用于图像分类、文本分类、推荐系统等应用的模型。
        在我的空闲时间，我也喜欢健身和旅游。我认为健身可以帮助我保持身体健康，旅游则可以帮助我放松身心，在忙碌的工作后获得新的思路和灵感。
        感谢您花时间了解我，我期待着和您交流和合作！
      </p>
      <p>English:</p>
      <p>
        Hello everyone, I'm zouhangwithsweet, a software engineer from China currently living in the San Francisco Bay
        Area in the United States. My main work is developing and maintaining large-scale cloud-based application
        systems. I have many years of experience in software development and have mastered various programming
        languages, such as Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript. In addition to my career, I am also interested in artificial
        intelligence. I am currently learning machine learning and deep learning, and sharing my learning notes and
        projects on my GitHub, including models for image classification, text classification, recommendation systems,
        and more. In my free time, I also enjoy working out and traveling. I believe that working out can help me stay
        healthy, and traveling can help me relax and gain new perspectives and inspiration after busy work. Thank you
        for taking the time to get to know me, and I look forward to connecting and collaborating with you!
      </p>
      <em style="text-align: right; margin-left: auto; display: block; font-weight: bold;">via: ChatGPT</em>
      <p class="underline">
        Contact me if you have a remote job <a href="mailto:zouhangsweet@gmail.com">Send me an Email</a>.
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
